Permissions and Copyright

The Yale School of Management Stock Market Confidence Indexes, and related
material, is produced and copyrighted by the International Center of Finance
at the Yale School of Management, Yale University, unless otherwise noted.
The information available on our site may not be reproduced or distributed
without written permission from the International Center for Finance at the
Yale School of Management.
If you would like to request permission to publish any of the material
on this site, please send your request to leigh.clark@yale.edu.

Your request should include a complete citation of the material you would like
to publish, or the additional data you wish to obtain.
We only permit summaries of the material to be published, and not the raw data
and related material itself.
